Features
````````

*	app name, path, bundle support
*	case insensitive (name, path)


Examples
````````


.. code:: bash

	$ app-pid "iTunes"
	294
	
	$ app-pid "iTunes.app"
	294
	
	$ app-pid "com.apple.iTunes" # bundle
	294
	
	$ app-pid "unknown" &> /dev/null && echo "running" || echo "not running"
